rComments: I have never had such a good prof! His way of teaching is excellent.

Seemed he assigns you a grade the very first time he sees you, and no matter how great your work is, you can't escape your fate! He told me before I even started my assignment that I could never get an A!

whenever I went to see him, he confused me more by going round about and not coming to a clear point. I agree he is smart but he can be soooo confusing at times! I DO NOT recommend you to take this course unless if u have certain desires of making your 4 months semester experience complicated and miserable!
He's not warm and fuzzy but he knows his stuff. I class worth taking if you're interested in changing your view of the world!
Great prof! Completely changed my perspective of things. If you ever get a chance to take a course with him I HIGHLY recommend it!
The only saving grace in the faculty of education!!!!
